overview.en: GOMC is a token issued by the SINGAPORE GGUMTHEC LIMITED platform with a total distribution of 1 billion and guaranteed never to be added, and GOMC is the decentral block chain digital asset issued on ETH. It is based on the ETH ERC 20 standard token.
overview.zh: GOMC是SINGAPORE GGUMTHEC LIMITED平台发行的代币，其发行总量为10亿个，且保证永不增发，GOMC是应用以太坊发行的去中心化的区块链数字资产，它是基于以太坊区块链的ERC 20标准代币。
